    {% endslide %}
    {% slide %}
        <p>But the biggest impact we can have is to make systemic changes, using {% ext "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Climate_movement#Activities" %}collective{% endext %}, {% ext "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carbon_tax" %}economic{% endext %}, {% ext "https://www.simonandschuster.com/books/On-Fire/Naomi-Klein/9781982129910" %}political{% endext %}, and {% ext "https://www.unep.org/news-and-stories/story/battle-against-climate-change-courts-become-new-frontier" %}legal{% endext %} actions.</p>
    {% endslide %}
    {% slide %}
